data.description: Welcome Home!! This 3 bedroom 2 bath located in a gated community with a park. Enjoy the inviting entry with high ceilings throughout the home. Charming kitchen with island, breakfast bar, plenty of cabinet space, tile flooring, pantry and desk area. Big master bed with large walk-in closet. Great size bedrooms that share lovely bath with tub/shower combo so clean up will be a breeze! Small backyard with lots of potential.
